Iterator Maven Plugin


* Overview

  The <{{{./executor-mojo.html}executor}}> goal is intended to call a maven plugin.
  
  Let us take a look at a real example which makes explanations simpler. We have the following 
  layout of the project:


+----------
.
├── dev.xml
├── pom.xml
├── prod.xml
├── test.xml
└── src
    ├── main
    │   ├── java
    │   ├──   ...
    │   └── resources
    │       └── log4j.properties
    └── test
        └── java
               ...
+----------

